name: Holiday Vacation Rentals
overview: Holiday Vacation Rentals has a variety of cottages, condos, and fine vacation residences in Northern Michigan. Our many convenient locations are close to area attractions, summer festivals, winter sports, shopping, and local dining. Rentals are available for families, couples, and large groups. Take a golf vacation at Birchwood County Club or pamper yourself at the LeBear Luxury Residential Club and Spa. Waterfront rentals are available on Lake Michigan, Burt Lake, Little Traverse Bay, Torch Lake and more! Rentals are priced at all levels of affordability. Vacation Protector Insurance is available for peace of mind against unexpected travel interruption. Visit our website or call a reservation specialist to learn why more guests are choosing Holiday Vacation Rentals for the keys to their next vacation getaway.
